# CI Gates

## After each AGENT step (Sprint TM / features)

```powershell
.\scripts\watch-agent-gates.ps1 -Once -Step tmN
```

## Gate order (local, Windows-primary)

1. `scripts/watch-agent-gates.ps1 -Once -Step <label>`
2. `scripts/validate-bootstrap.ps1 -Quick` (scaffold/doc changes)
3. `scripts/smoke/m0_smoke.ps1` + `scripts/smoke/m2_smoke.ps1` (product changes)
4. `scripts/run-milestone-gate.ps1 -Milestone N` (milestone sign-off)
5. Push → `scripts/check-github-ci.ps1 -WaitSeconds 300` (when installed, TM.P3)

## Do not mark complete

- BUILD_PLAN `[AGENT]` / `[AUTO]` items while CI is red
- TM sprint steps without `validate-bootstrap.ps1` pass
- Pipeline changes without `verify-tone-quality.ps1` when golden fixtures apply

Push to remote requires `[HUMAN]` approval per `destructive-ops.mdc`.
